spans.text: No Grandeur was above the reach of Woe
if Affluence spreads her gaudy Wings
some secret Method find To view the dark Recesses of the Mind
A cankerous Venom on the Vitals preys
all the Comforts of his Days
the Hand that gives the Blow
An ample Recompense for all his Pains
of a prosperous Fate The pious Fervours of the Soul abate
The pious Fervours of the Soul
secret Ends , Corroding Cares , or sharp Affliction
